{"tid":2321694,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件拯救失眠嘅法寶","createTime":"2020-12-11T16:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T01:28:24.000Z","uid":221401,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"ffe909040ccb131b513e29fcf0a5f43fe9425666","tid":2321694,"uid":221401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:53:35.000Z","msg":"已經俾失眠困擾咗兩年<br />\n一諗到聽朝有重要事做或者要早起就訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最高紀錄三日一秒都冇訓過<br />\n有時就算訓到都好，都會四五點就醒然後眼光光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有一排要晩晩食鎮靜劑訓，但我知長此下去唔係辦法，所以轉咗食melatonin，嗰隻牌子1粒3mg 最多食3粒，所以如果訓唔到嘅時候我就會食3粒，但好多時候我食完都係訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想問下大家有冇方法可以訓得好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed9777de6423717b9f919ac393e6c42a0256687","tid":2321694,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:56:40.000Z","msg":"有冇check過sleeping quality <br />\n我講緊畀錢check嗰啲"},{"pid":"5d194ffb48f762747d494b1b58f5cc4add179435","tid":2321694,"uid":245910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T16:57:42.000Z","msg":"石頭"},{"pid":"73e012473fd582109a8f6bc4bd5fccff3e22caf7","tid":2321694,"uid":346584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:04:18.000Z","msg":"有冇試過催眠<br />\n上YouTube 聽催眠音樂就瞓到"},{"pid":"9e2a07fad3a9eb5f563b5ae553b08a39065b9d3b","tid":2321694,"uid":137569,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:08:24.000Z","msg":"我有時都失眠<br />\n同自己講<br />\n瞓唔著只要唔郁<br />\n都係休息"},{"pid":"9e74a18004e93fdd963848eb92ac22c2267f4768","tid":2321694,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:11:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PgkvwG971hw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPgkvwG971hw&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=473f963b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PgkvwG971hw</a>"},{"pid":"a6bdbd6211fcdef3c86f4523719ddc65098837ca","tid":2321694,"uid":227588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:13:13.000Z","msg":"同老豆/阿媽傾計"},{"pid":"d0bb7457851d6d437d51895f871848d387f58fc7","tid":2321694,"uid":208940,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:16:44.000Z","msg":"信我，聽劉細良節目，好快入睡"},{"pid":"8028d1444f8b276b0449e53fc607a47eb4bc5620","tid":2321694,"uid":227588,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:23:06.000Z","msg":"認真，試吓聽收音機，聲音教細d，儘量放鬆自己。<br />\n真係瞓唔到、瞓唔返，索性起身做d嘢⋯<br />\n唔好太依賴藥物，同埋唔好令瞓覺都變成壓力。"},{"pid":"d5a2b29f66d469c0b2fc2c9810a493f02c248bb1","tid":2321694,"uid":357436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e2a07fad3a9eb5f563b5ae553b08a39065b9d3b","tid":2321694,"uid":137569,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:08:24.000Z","msg":"我有時都失眠<br />\n同自己講<br />\n瞓唔著只要唔郁<br />\n都係休息"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:24:29.000Z","msg":"同我諗法一樣"},{"pid":"1110d455409274077fdbff5cf262e599a37c34f4","tid":2321694,"uid":367811,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2798ee3e222b5db0f9af55ede992793d5a4ea1b","tid":2321694,"uid":18040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:28:07.000Z","msg":"melatonin"},{"pid":"5bd7debbde357afc3d358cd9a60c828d09f9f91d","tid":2321694,"uid":58002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:31:08.000Z","msg":"運動"},{"pid":"be27401af1c071296283a4e8e638b074e431e555","tid":2321694,"uid":11442,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T17:35:06.000Z","msg":"我有排好焦慮會失眠<br />\n試過噴Do姐<br />\n效果都唔錯"},{"pid":"4ece8efc5118174c0166cd7748845ff60f94ec15","tid":2321694,"uid":221401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ed9777de6423717b9f919ac393e6c42a0256687","tid":2